## 4 / 6 — Speed Skaters
**40 seconds · Low and fast**

- Lateral bound off one foot — land on the opposite foot
- Trail leg sweeps **behind**, not beside
- Reach opposite hand toward landing foot
- Stay **low** — don't pop up between bounds
- Drive the arms for momentum

**Target:** 22–28 bounds in 40s
**Common fault:** Staying upright — get that hip hinge, chest forward, eyes ahead

